Package parser

Class LineMatcher

  • java.lang.Object
    • parser.LineMatcher
  • public class LineMatcher
extends java.lang.Object
    Simple class which main task is to calculate regular expressions and use them. This class was made so the patterns are compiled only once but used many times (big time of compilation). It's mainly used to distinguish type of line read by parser.
